headline: Essex Announces Release and Conference Call Dates for Its First Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., April 04, 2025--Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) announced today that it plans to release its first quarter 2025 earnings after the market closes on Tuesday, April 29, 2025. A conference call with senior management is scheduled for Wednesday, April 30, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. Pacific Time or 12:00 p.m. Eastern Time.

headline: Essex Property Updates YTD Portfolio Reallocation Activity
summary: ESS invests in long-term value-accretive assets in submarkets with potential less supply and higher rental growth and disposes of non-core assets.
